pathfinding

Class NodePair

  • java.lang.Object
    • pathfinding.NodePair
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NodeData

    public class NodePair
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used internally for the pathfinding algorithms. It stores a pair of nodes and a reference to the next node used by the PairList class, and also the depth of the pair.
